THE GAME
--------

  'Interferium' is a Workbench game where you have to connect all
tiles that are of the same type. To do so you have to make a
'path' from one tile and make your way to another tile. But
beware, there are some other tiles on the game board, so it is up
to you to make paths that will let the other tiles be connected
without interference...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

